videoSnippet.title: Don't Make Your Life Miserable (Like Me) -  Know Your Openings!
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Here is a game from Round 4 Of Križevci Chess Club Championship I played today. Some interesting variation happened in the game :) Last year I won first place, winning all games and drawing one. So far I'm 4/4, 3 more games to go.
Time control was 90min + 30 sec increment per move.
I missed some better continuations, but, that's why we analyze games :)

Antonio Radić vs Goran Martić
Križevci Chess Club Championship 2018., Križevci, Croatia, rd 4, Feb-10 
Sicilian Defense: Scheveningen (B86)

1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 d6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 a6 6. Bc4 e6 7. Bb3 Nbd7 8. O-O Nc5 9. Re1 Qc7 10. Bg5 b5 11. Nd5 Nxd5 12. exd5 e5 13. f4 Nxb3 14. cxb3 Be7 15. Rc1 Qd7 16. Bxe7 Qxe7 17. fxe5 O-O 18. Nc6 Qh4 19. exd6 Qf6 20. Ne7+ Kh8 21. Nxc8 Raxc8 22. Rxc8 Rxc8 23. d7 Rf8 24. Re8
